quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,70,"Àfi ẹni tí ó bá ronú pìwàdà, tí ó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí ó sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni Allāhu yóò fi iṣẹ́ rere rọ́pò iṣẹ́ aburú wọn (ìyẹn, nípa ìronúpìwàdà wọn). Allāhu sì ń jẹ́ Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  25,71,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ronú pìwàdà, tí ó sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, (kí ó mọ̀) pé dájúdájú ó ń ronú pìwàdà pátápátá sọ́dọ̀ Allāhu ni."
  25,72,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tí kò jẹ́rìí èké. Tí wọ́n bá sì kọjá níbi ìbàjẹ́, wọ́n á kọjá pẹ̀lú àpọ́nlé.{1}.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu ń pọ́nra wọn lé nípa àìjókòó pọ̀ pẹ̀lú àwọn onísọkúsọ. Wọ́n sì ń pọ́nra wọn lé nípa yíyẹra fún ìjókòó tí àwọn aláìmọ̀kan bá ti ń ṣe ìbàjẹ̀ nínú rẹ̀.]
  26,43,"(Ànábì) Mūsā sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ ju ohun tí ẹ fẹ́ jù sílẹ̀.”"
  26,44,"Wọ́n sì ju àwọn okùn wọn àti ọ̀pá wọn sílẹ̀. Wọ́n wí pé: “Pẹ̀lú ògo Fir‘aon, dájúdájú àwa, àwa ni olùborí.”"
  26,45,"Nígbà náà, (Ànábì) Mūsā ju ọ̀pá rẹ̀ sílẹ̀. Ó sì ń gbé ohun tí wọ́n pa nírọ́ kalẹ̀ mì kálókáló."
  27,16,"(Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n sì jogún (Ànábì) Dāwūd. Ó sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn, Wọ́n fi ohùn ẹyẹ mọ̀ wá. Wọ́n sì fún wa nínú gbogbo n̄ǹkan.{1} Dájúdájú èyí, òhun ni oore àjùlọ pọ́nńbélé.”.",1:[Àgbọ́yé gbólóhùn yìí “Wọ́n sì fún wa nínú gbogbo n̄ǹkan.” ni pé, wọ́n fún àwọn méjèèjì ní ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ n̄ǹkan nínú oore ayé.]
  27,17,"A sì kó jọ fún (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n, àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀ nínú àlùjànnú, ènìyàn àti ẹyẹ. A sì ń kó wọn jọ papọ̀ mọ́ra wọn sí ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀ tí wọ́n ń bá a rìn káàkiri"
  27,18,"títí wọ́n fi dé àfonúfojì àwọn àwúrèbe. Àwúrèbe kan sì wí pé: “Ẹ̀yin àwúrèbe, ẹ wọ inú ilé yín lọ, kí (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n àti àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀ má baà tẹ̀ yín rẹ́ mọ́lẹ̀. Wọn kò sì níí furamọ̀.”"